%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnymag.com%2Fintelligencer%2Farticle%2Fhunter-biden-laptop-investigation.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworked%20with%20Bannon%20to%20disseminate%20the%20contents%20of%20Hunter%20Biden's%20laptop%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Morris%20told%20BI%20she%20hadn't%20seen%20any%20of%20Bannon's%20other%20Epstein%20footage%20and%20didn't%20know%20what%20happened%20to%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBannon's%20time%20in%20Epstein's%20orbit%20was%20recounted%20in%20the%20book%20%26quot%3BToo%20Famous%2C%26quot%3B%20published%20in%20October%202021%20by%20Michael%20Wolff%2C%20who%20heavily%20relied%20on%20Bannon%20as%20a%20source%20for%20his%20books%20about%20Trump's%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20section%20titled%20%26quot%3BMonster%2C%26quot%3B%20Wolff%20wrote%20that%20Bannon%20sought%20to%20change%20the%20public%20perception%20of%20Epstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBannon%20believed%20Epstein%20needed%20a%20public-facing%20communications%20strategy%20in%20response%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.miamiherald.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Farticle220097825.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJulie%20K.%20Brown's%20%26quot%3BPerversion%20of%20Justice%26quot%3B%20series%20in%20the%20Miami%20Herald%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Brown%20reported%20Alexander%20Acosta%2C%20who%2C%20as%20a%20US%20attorney%20in%20Florida%20in%20the%202000s%2C%20oversaw%20a%20criminal%20investigation%20into%20the%20financier%2C%20arranged%20a%20light%20plea%20deal%20even%20though%20law-enforcement%20agents%20were%20aware%20that%20Epstein%20had%20abused%20dozens%20of%20girls.%20Acosta%20resigned%20from%20his%20position%20as%20labor%20secretary%20in%20the%20Trump%20administration%20following%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWolff's%20book%20says%20that%20in%20a%20March%202019%20conference%20call%2C%20Bannon%2C%20Epstein%2C%20former%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Ehud%20Barak%2C%20and%20Epstein's%20defense%20attorney%20Reid%20Weingarten%20discussed%20whether%20Epstein%20should%20give%20a%20primetime%20TV%20interview.%20They%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-got-media-training-from-steve-bannon-report-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efloated%20the%20idea%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20going%20on%20CBS's%20%26quot%3B60%20Minutes%26quot%3B%20or%20interviewing%20with%20Rachel%20Maddow%20or%20Gayle%20King%2C%20Wolff%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20Wolff%20wrote%2C%20Epstein%20%26quot%3Bmade%20the%20gesture%20of%20the%20noose%20above%20his%20head%26quot%3B%20to%20express%20his%20distaste%20at%20the%20idea%20of%20being%20interviewed%20by%20King.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224499%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Steve%20Bannon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62daecdf6fb3cf0018e08519%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20Trump%20White%20House%20advisor%20Steve%20Bannon.%3Cp%3EPatrick%20Semansky%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20book%2C%20Bannon%20said%20that%20recording%20videos%20would%20help%20Epstein%20prepare%20for%20an%20interview%20that%20would%20convince%20the%20world%20%26quot%3Bhe's%20not%20a%20monster.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20got%20to%20sit%20there%20and%20watch%20the%20tape%20all%20the%20time%2C%20that's%20how%20you%20learn%2C%26quot%3B%20Bannon%20said%2C%20according%20to%20Wolff.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20like%20preparing%20for%20a%20deposition%2C%20except%20this%20is%20preparing%20for%20the%20court%20of%20public%20opinion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWolff's%20book%20includes%20long%20excerpts%20of%20conversations%20between%20Epstein%20and%20Bannon%2C%20as%20well%20as%20descriptions%20of%20Epstein's%20activities%20during%20the%20time%20he%20was%20close%20with%20Bannon.%20The%20book%20does%20not%20disclose%20whether%20Wolff%20viewed%20Bannon's%20footage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuotes%20in%20the%20book%20suggest%20that%20during%20sit-down%20interviews%20with%20Bannon%2C%20Epstein%20created%20an%20air%20of%20mystery%3A%20He%20was%20evasive%20about%20his%20interactions%20with%20girls%2C%20declined%20to%20name%20the%20wealthy%20people%20he%20advised%20on%20financial%20issues%2C%20and%20said%20he'd%20%26quot%3Bescorted%26quot%3B%20Princess%20Diana%20%26quot%3Bon%20occasion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBannon%20also%20said%20he%20believed%20Epstein%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bintelligence%20asset%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20it%20doesn't%20describe%20any%20evidence%20he%20offered%20to%20support%20the%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBannon%2C%20who%20was%20the%20chairman%20of%20Trump's%202016%20presidential%20campaign%2C%20believed%20Epstein%20knew%20%26quot%3Bdangerous%20secrets%20about%20Trump%2C%26quot%3B%20Wolff%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20were%20the%20only%20person%20I%20was%20afraid%20of%20during%20the%20campaign%2C%26quot%3B%20Bannon%20told%20Epstein%2C%20according%20to%20Wolff's%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWolff%20wrote%20that%20Epstein%20said%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bregaled%20him%20with%20the%20torrid%20details%26quot%3B%20of%20his%20sexual%20encounter%20with%20E.%20Jean%20Carroll%20in%20Bergdorf%20Goodman%20in%20the%20mid-1990s.%20A%20civil%20jury%20last%20year%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-liable-rape-e-jean-carroll-jury-verdict-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%20Trump%20liable%20for%20sexually%20abusing%20Carroll%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Manhattan%20department%20store%20and%20defaming%20her%20by%20lying%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWolff%20wrote%20that%20Bannon%20also%20appeared%20skeptical%20of%20Epstein's%20many%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCome%20on%2C%20dude.%20This%20is%20a%20stinking%20fish.%26quot%3B%20Bannon%20told%20his%20camera%20operator%2C%20according%20to%20Wolff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGod%2C%20it's%20all%20such%20bullshit.%20Nothing%20makes%20any%20sense%20in%20this%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20reportedly%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhich%20is%20what%20makes%20it%20so%20fucking%20compelling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-bannon-filmed-jeffrey-epstein-trump-friendship-documentary-tapes-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721219642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668d4468098114dafd1a9e36%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-bannon-filmed-jeffrey-epstein-trump-friendship-documentary-tapes-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20staunch%20Donald%20Trump%20ally%20said%20his%20Epstein%20tapes%20were%20meant%20for%20a%20documentary.%20People%20who%20knew%20them%20together%20say%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20help%20Epstein.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jshamsian%40businessinsider.com%20(Jacob%20Shamsian)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-bannon-filmed-jeffrey-epstein-trump-friendship-documentary-tapes-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Haryana%20govt%20announces%2010%25%20job%20reservation%20for%20Agniveers%3B%20key%20details%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721218414000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-05%2F23%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1716472362-2173.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fpolitics%2Fharyana-govt-announces-10-job-reservation-for-agniveers-key-details-124071700702_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20reservation%20includes%20a%2010%20per%20cent%20horizontal%20quota%20for%20Agniveers%20in%20the%20posts%20of%20constable%2C%20mining%20guard%2C%20forest%20guard%2C%20jail%20warden%2C%20and%20SPO%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fpolitics%2Fharyana-govt-announces-10