revamp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20discussed%20key%20organisation%20issues%20with%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20BJP%20president.%20The%20BJP%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20is%20keen%20on%20having%20an%20OBC%20leader%20as%20its%20state%20chief%20as%20it%20preps%20to%20bounce%20back%20from%20the%20poll%20setback%20and%20prepare%20for%20the%202027%20state%20polls.%20The%20incumbent%2C%20Mr%20Chaudhary%2C%20is%20a%20Jat%20leader%20from%20Moradabad%20and%20was%C2%A0given%20the%20role%20in%202022%20to%20quell%20the%20resentment%20against%20BJP%20within%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20possible%20choice%20of%20an%20OBC%20leader%20to%20replace%20Mr%20Chaudhary%20may%20be%20explained%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20OBCs%20account%20for%20a%20sizeable%20chunk%20of%20the%20state's%20population%20and%20are%20a%20key%20factor%20in%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20suffered%20a%20big%20debacle%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%20this%20general%20election%2C%20with%20its%20score%20dropping%20from%2062%20in%202019%20to%2033%20this%20time%20as%20main%20Opposition%20Samajwadi%20Party%20made%20big%20gains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20won%20the%20last%20two%20state%20polls%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20will%20leave%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20score%20a%20hat-trick.%20So%2C%20wide%20and%20big%20changes%20in%20the%20party%20organisation%20are%20likely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Backdrop%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeculation%20over%20an%20organisational%20overhaul%20come%20against%20the%20Opposition's%20claims%20of%20infighting%20within%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government%20in%20the%20state.%20This%20buzz%20was%20sparked%20by%20a%20remark%20by%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Maurya%20during%20a%20party%20meeting%20on%20Sunday.%20%26quot%3BThe%20organisation%20is%20bigger%20than%20the%20government.%20No%20one%20is%20bigger%20than%20the%20organisation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Maurya%20said.%20The%20remark%20was%20widely%20seen%20as%20a%20veiled%20swipe%20at%20Chief%20Minister%20Adityanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELatching%20on%20to%20the%20remark%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%20people%20of%20the%20state%20are%20suffering%20due%20to%20infighting%20within%20the%20state%20government.%20%26quot%3BBJP%20leaders%20are%20fighting%20among%20themselves.%20The%20people%20know%20about%20the%20corruption%20and%20are%20fed%20up%20with%20the%20game%20of%20thrones%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%2C%20however%2C%20dismissed%20the%20infighting%20buzz.%20Responding%20to%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%2C%20Mr%20Maurya%20tweeted%20this%20afternoon%20that%20the%20BJP's%20governments%20and%20organisation%20in%20the%20country%20and%20the%20state%20are%20strong.%20%26quot%3BThe%20return%20of%20SP's%20reign%20of%20goons%20in%20UP%20is%20impossible.%20BJP%20will%20repeat%202017%20in%20the%202027%20state%20polls%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20X.%20Significantly%2C%20Mr%20Maurya%20was%20state%20BJP%20chief%20in%202017%20and%20the%20BJP%20had%20scored%20a%20thumping%20win%20in%20that%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20potent%20remark%20at%20the%20BJP%20state%20executive%20meeting%2C%20Mr%20Adityanath%20had%20said%20%26quot%3Boverconfidence%26quot%3B%20cost%20the%20party%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20%26quot%3BThe%20percentage%20of%20votes%20that%20was%20in%20favour%20of%20BJP%20in%202014%20and%20subsequent%20elections%2C%20BJP%20has%20been%20successful%20in%20getting%20the%20same%20number%20of%20votes%20in%202024%20as%20well%2C%20but%20the%20shifting%20of%20votes%20and%20overconfidence%20have%20hurt%20our%20expectations%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adityanath%20said%2C%20calling%20upon%20party%20workers%20to%20step%20up%20preparations%20for%20the%20upcoming%20bypolls.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721217480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fir2r4jdo_modi-shah_625x300_29_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22ori