cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fglenmark-pharma-receives-usfda-approval-for-seizure-treatment-drug-124071700684_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fglenmark-pharma-receives-usfda-approval-for-seizure-treatment-drug-124071700684_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Government%20Must%20Take%20Blame%20For%20Allowing%20To%20Cut%20422%20Trees%3A%20Top%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20has%20shown%20lack%20of%20sensitivity%20over%20protecting%20the%20environment%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20while%20rapping%20it%20for%20granting%20permission%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Development%20Authority%20to%20chop%20422%20trees%20in%20the%20Southern%20Ridge's%20reserve%20forest%20area%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20justices%20Abhay%20S%20Oka%20and%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20said%20it%20is%20an%20admitted%20position%20as%20reflected%20in%20the%20statement%20made%20by%20the%20tree%20officer%20that%20for%20felling%20422%20trees%2C%20the%20officer%20did%20not%20grant%20any%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20was%20hearing%20suo%20motu%20(on%20its%20own)%20contempt%20proceedings%20against%20the%20vice%20chairman%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Development%20Authority%20(DDA)%20over%20alleged%20cutting%20of%201%2C100%20trees%20in%20the%20ridge%20forest%20for%20a%20road%20widening%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Delhi%20government%20must%20take%20the%20blame%20for%20granting%20permission%20to%20fell%20422%20trees%2C%20though%20there%20was%20no%20statutory%20power%20vesting%20in%20the%20Delhi%20government%20to%20grant%20such%20permission%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%20in%20an%20order%20dated%20July%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThus%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20trees%20in%20the%20ridge%20area%2C%20the%20government%20facilitated%20cutting%20and%20felling%20the%20trees%20outside%20the%20ridge%20area%20without%20permission%20under%20the%20Delhi%20Preservation%20of%20Trees%20Act%2C%201994%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20said%2C%20like%20the%20DDA%2C%20the%20Delhi%20government%20has%20shown%20a%20lack%20of%20sensitivity%20over%20protecting%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20the%20Delhi%20government%20has%20not%20even%20provided%20the%20tree%20officer%20and%20the%20Tree%20Authority%20an%20office%20or%20basic%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20must%20come%20before%20the%20court%20and%20tell%20%26quot%3Bhow%20it%20will%20compensate%20for%20the%20damage%20caused%20to%20the%20environment%20due%20to%20its%20illegal%20acts%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20affidavit%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government%20also%20shows%20that%20this%20is%20not%20the%20only%20instance%20where%20the%20forest%20department%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government%20purported%20to%20grant%20permission%20for%20the%20felling%20of%20trees.%20They%20had%20done%20it%20earlier%20also%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government's%20stand%20is%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20DDA%20has%20accepted%20that%20they%20misread%20the%20notifications%20issued%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20will%20not%20absolve%20the%20Delhi%20government%20of%20its%20responsibility%20of%20passing%20orders%20permitting%20the%20felling%20of%20trees%2C%20though%20no%20statutory%20power%20is%20vested%20in%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20said%20the%20Delhi%20government%20must%20also%20come%20out%20with%20an%20action%20taken%20report%2C%20if%20any%2C%20against%20the%20erring%20officers%20who%20are%20alleged%20to%20have%20granted%20permissions%20for%20the%20felling%20of%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApart%20from%20a%20statement%20on%20oath%20which%20we%20expect%20the%20Delhi%20government%20to%20make%20about%20compensating%20the%20loss%20caused%20to%20the%20environment%2C%20we%20hope%20and%20trust%20that%20the%20Delhi%20government%20will%20immediately%20stop%20exercising%20the%20non-existent%20power%20of%20granting%20permissions%20for%20the%20felling%20of%20trees%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20do%20so%2C%20we%20direct%20the%20Delhi%20government%20to%20ascertain%20how%20many%20such%20permissions%20have%20been%20granted%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%20and%20place%20all%20those%20permissions%20on%20record.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20the%20top%20court%20expressed%20anguish%20over%20continuous%20%26quot%3Bcover%20up%26quot%3B%20by%20authorities%20over%20the%20role%20of%20Delhi%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20in%20tree%20felling%20in%20the%20ridge%20area%20and%20directed%20the%20DDA%20to%20inform%20it%20whether%20the%20order%20to%20cut%20trees%20was%20passed%20on%20basis%20of%20the%20LG's%20oral%20permission%20or%20the%20DDA%20independently%20took%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Aditya%20Sondhi%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20assured%20the%20court%20that%20office%20infrastructure%2C%20staff%20and%20necessary%20hardware%20and%20software%20will%20be%20made%20available%20to%20the%20Tree%20Authority%20and%20the%20tree%20officer%20within%20six%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Delhi%20government%20shall%20also%20ensure%20that%20the%20Tree%20Authority%20is%20properly%20constituted%20before%20the%20next%20date.%20Regarding%20the%20forest%20department%20of%20the%20state%20government%2C%20the%20entire%20infrastructure%20must%20be%20put%20in%20place%20within%20two%20months%20from%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Delhi%20government%20must%20file%20an%20affidavit%20indicating%20what%2