%2010%20on%20the%20happiness%20scale.%20I%20completely%20understand%20why%2C%20especially%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-lithuania-world-happiest-country-for-gen-z-millennials-education-2024-6%23%3A~%3Atext%3DLithuania%2520was%2520ranked%2520the%2520happiest%2Cin%2520tech%2520and%2520creative%2520fields.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyoung%20person%20living%20in%20Vilnius%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22703f0fa1-23bb-4ae9-a696-e0a271b0c704%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EYoung%20people%20can%20study%20for%20free%20in%20Lithuania%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20in%20high%20school%2C%20most%20classmates%20planned%20to%20either%20learn%20a%20trade%20in%20college%20or%20go%20to%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20funds%20higher%20education%20in%20public%20institutions.%20As%20long%20as%20you%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feurydice.eacea.ec.europa.eu%2Fnational-education-systems%2Flithuania%2Fhigher-education-funding%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520order%2520to%2520apply%2520for%2Cforeign%2520language%2520and%2520maths%2520exams.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epass%20your%20national%20exams%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20high%20school%2C%20you%20can%20apply%20to%20a%20state-funded%20university%20with%20free%20tuition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20our%20degrees%20are%20specialized%2C%20you%20can%20still%20change%20your%20mind%20and%20switch%20degrees.%20I%20initially%20studied%20creativity%20communication%20but%20changed%20my%20mind.%20Because%20I'd%20completed%20less%20than%20half%20of%20my%20credits%20for%20the%20degree%2C%20I%20could%20still%20switch%20to%20a%20new%20bachelor's%20and%20complete%20it%20free%20of%20charge.%20This%20is%20the%20standard%20practice%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-european-universities-2014-2014-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELithuanian%20universities%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Our%20education%20system%20didn't%20put%20me%20in%20a%20box