er%20worried%20about%20money%20on%20my%20digital%20advertising%20salary.%20I%20ordered%20takeaway%20for%20most%20dinners%20and%20never%20turned%20down%20a%20social%20event%20for%20money%20reasons.%20I've%20still%20been%20able%20to%20travel%20to%20western%20countries%20as%20well%20as%20to%20cheaper%20destinations%20in%20Eastern%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20briefly%20lived%20in%20America%20and%20other%20European%20countries%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20everything%20seemed%20really%20high%20compared%20to%20Vilnius.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20find%20a%20place%20to%20rent%20on%20my%20own%20in%20Vilnius%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.aruodas.lt%2Fbutu-nuoma-vilniuje-naujamiestyje-sv-stepono-g-isnuomojamas-kvm-ploto-kambario-4-1327510%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E600%20euros%20a%20month%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Although%20I'm%20not%20looking%20to%20buy%20a%20house%2C%20my%20parents%20bought%20a%20two-bedroom%20apartment%20eight%20years%20ago%20for%20around%2080%2C000%20euros.%20House%20prices%20are%20more%20expensive%20now%2C%20but%20still%20cheaper%20than%20in%20other%20European%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20out%20with%20friends%20is%20cheap%2C%20making%20for%20a%20great%20social%20life.%20A%20beer%20costs%20five%20euros%2C%20and%20an%20average%20restaurant%20meal%20costs%2010%20euros.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20single%20person%2C%20I%20can%20spend%20as%20little%20as%2040%20euros%20a%20week%20on%20groceries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friends%20and%20I%20attend%20several%20concerts%20or%20festivals%20a%20month%20because%20they%20are%20either%20free%20or%20very%20cheap.%20Nightclub%20entry%20is%20often%2010%20euros%20or%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2296a13632-8d6c-43bf-85ee-5b41697a8631%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20capital%20city%20is%20lively%20and%20inclusive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAutumn%20and%20winter%20can%20be%20very%20cold%20in%20Lithuania.%20People%20get%20excited%20by%20the%20first%20snowfall%20of%20the%20year%2C%20but%20they%20also%20tend%20to%20socialize%20less%20than%20they%20do%20in%20the%20spring%20and%20summer.%20The%20occasional%20person%20experiences%20seasonal%20depression%20when%20the%20seasons%20change%2C%20and%20people%20go%20out%20less%2C%20but%20most%20appreciate%20this%20calmer%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Vilnius%2C%20outdoor%20caf%C3%A9s%20stretch%20throughout%20the%20Old%20Town%2C%20with%20people%20catching%20up%20over%20espresso%20that%20is%20just%20as%20good%20as%20in%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mix%20of%20city%20and%20nature%20is%20perfectly%20balanced.%20There%20are%20beautiful%20outdoor%20areas%2C%20and%20I%20run%20in%20the%20woods%20every%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20summer%2C%20my%20friends%20and%20I%20flock%20to%20one%20of%20the%20many%20lakes%20scattered%20around%20Vilnius.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20is%20home%20to%20many%20young%20people%20and%20is%20more%20multicultural%20than%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20so%20it%20feels%20more%20open%20to%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20member%20of%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20community%2C%20I%20find%20Vilnius%20very%20safe.%20People%20from%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20community%20move%20to%20the%20city%20because%20it's%20a%20younger%2C%20more%20accepting%20demographic%2C%20and%20the%20culture%20is%20more%20vibrant%20here.%20Living%20in%20a%20post-Soviet%20country%2C%20it's%20difficult%20to%20change%20the%20views%20of%20older%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2277c445d2-6c3e-4e88-bb73-b0bad6523b1b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20prefer%20Vilnius%20to%20other%20places%20I've%20lived%20as%20a%20young%20person%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20my%20country.%20I%20have%20lived%20elsewhere%2C%20including%20in%20Portugal%2C%20America%2C%20and%20Italy%2C%20but%20I%20always%20wanted%20to%20return%20to%20Vilnius.%20I%20missed%20the%20hipster%20bars%2C%20Lithuanian%20craft%20beer%2C%20and%20the%20forest%20greenery.%20It%20is%20the%20happiest%20place%20for%20me%20as%20a%20young%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20