d%20plan%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20as%20it%20leads%20to%20skilled%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Saini%20said%20that%20in%20Group%20C%20and%20D%20posts%2C%20an%20age%20relaxation%20of%20three%20years%20will%20also%20be%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20in%20the%20first%20batch%20of%20Agniveers%2C%20this%20age%20relaxation%20will%20be%20five%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Saini%20said.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20private%20company%20pays%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%2030%2C000%20to%20an%20Agniveer%2C%20then%20the%20government%20will%20give%20an%20annual%20subsidy%20of%20Rs%2060%2C000%20to%20that%20company%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721213940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F7d0c2ue_agniveer-scheme_625x300_13_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-announces-10-quota-in-police-mining-guard-jobs-for-agniveers-6125244%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2010%20per%20cent%20reservation%20has%20been%20earmarked%20in%20police%20and%20mining%20guard%20jobs%20for%20Agniveers%2C%20announced%20Haryana%20Chief%20Minister%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20amid%20an%20escalating%20row%20over%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20Opposition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A41%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-announces-10-quota-in-police-mining-guard-jobs-for-agniveers-6125244%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-announces-10-quota-in-police-mining-guard-jobs-for-agniveers-6125244%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-announces-10-quota-in-police-mining-guard-jobs-for-agniveers-6125244%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karnataka%20Job%20Quota%20May%20Force%20%26quot%3BCompanies%20To%20Relocate%26quot%3B%3A%20Software%20Body%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20the%20Karnataka%20cabinet%20approved%20a%20bill%20mandating%20reservation%20for%20locals%20in%20the%20private%20sector%20jobs%2C%20software%20body%20Nasscom%20has%20sought%20its%20withdrawal%20saying%20the%20provisions%20%26quot%3Bthreaten%20to%20drive%20away%20companies%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20enforces%2050%20percent%20reservation%20for%20administrative%20posts%20and%2075%20percent%20for%20non-administrative%20posts%20for%20Kannadigas%20in%20private%20industries%20and%20has%20sparked%20controversy%20after%20it%20was%20announced%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20last%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENasscom%2C%20representing%20India's%20%24200%20billion%20technology%20industry%2C%20said%20the%20restrictions%20under%20the%20'Karnataka%20State%20Employment%20of%20Local%20Candidates%20in%20the%20Industries%2C%20Factories%20and%20Other%20Establishments%20Bill'%20could%20force%20companies%20to%20relocate%20as%20%26quot%3Blocal%20skilled%20talent%20becomes%20scarce%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bill's%20provisions%20threaten%20to%20drive%20away%20companies%2C%20and%20stifle%20startups%2C%20especially%20when%20more%20global%20firms%20(GCCs)%20are%20looking%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20state.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20restrictions%20could%20force%20companies%20to%20relocate%20as%20local%20skilled%20talent%20becomes%20scarce%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20IT%20industry's%20top%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contentious%20bill%2C%20on%20the%20appointment%20of%20'local%20candidates'%2C%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BAny%20industry%2C%20factory%20or%20other%20establishments%20shall%20appoint%20fifty%20per%20cent%20of%20local%20candidates%20in%20management%20categories%20and%20seventy%20per%20cent%20in%20non-management%20categories.%26quot%3B%20If%20the%20candidates%20do%20not%20possess%20a%20secondary%20school%20certificate%20with%20Kannada%20as%20a%20language%2C%20they%20must%20pass%20a%20Kannada%20proficiency%20test%20as%20specified%20by%20the%20'Nodal%20Agency'%2C%20it%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20is%20slated%20to%20be%20tabled%20in%20the%20Assembly%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20serious%20concerns%20about%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20bill%2C%20Nasscom%20urged%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20to%20withdraw%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20sought%20an%20urgent%20meeting%20of%20industry%20representatives%20with%20state%20authorities%20to%20discuss%20their%20concerns%20and%20%26quot%3Bprevent%20Karnataka's%20progress%20from%20being%20derailed%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlobally%2C%20there%20is%20a%20huge%20shortage%20of%20skilled%20talent%20and%20Karnataka%20despite%20the%20large%20pool%2C%20is%20no%20exception%2C%20the%20body%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20states%20to%20become%20a%20key%20technology%20hub%20a%20dual%20strategy%20is%20key%20-%20magnet%20for%20best%20talent%20worldwide%20and%20focussed%20investment%20in%20building%20a%20strong%20talent%20pool%20within%20the%20state%20through%20formal%20and%20vocational%20channels%2C%26quot%3B%20Nasscom%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20indicated%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20that%20the%20government%20would%20seek%20100%20percent%20reservation%20for%20Kannadigas%20in%20select%20categories.%20He%20later%20amended%20his%20post%20to%20omit%20the%20'100%20percent'%20provision%20after%20his%20post%20sparked%20a%20massive%20uproar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20asserted%20that%20it%20is%20the%20government's%20priority%20to%20look%20after%20the%20welfare%20of%20Kannadigas.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20our%20government's%20wish%20that%20the%20Kannadigas%20should%20avoid%20being%20deprived%20of%20jobs%20in%20the%20land%20of%20Kannada%20and%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20build%20a%20comfortable%20life%20in%20the%20motherland.%20We%20are%20a%20pro-Kannada%20government.%20Our%20priority%20is%20to%20look%20after%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20Kannadigas%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20industry%20leaders%20in%20the%20state%20objected%20to%20the%20move%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bdiscriminatory%26quot%3B%20and%20raised%20apprehensions%20that%20the%20tech%20industry%20may%20suffer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Commerce%20and%20Industries%20Minister%20MB%20Patil%20said%20that%20they%20will%20have%20wide%20consultations%20to%20resolve%20the%20confusion%20and%20ensure%20that%20the%20interests%20of%20Kannadigas%20are%20protected%20along%20with%20those%20of%20industries%20after%20industrialists%20expressed%20their%20apprehensions%20about%20the%20proposed%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Labor%20Minister%20Santosh%20S%20Lad%20also%20clarified%20that%20if%20adequate%20skills%20are%20not%20available%20in%20the%20state%2C%20people%20can%20be%20outsourced%20from%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20sector%20contributes%20almost%2025%20per%20cent%20of%20Karnataka's%20GDP%20and%20has%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20enabling%20higher%20growth%20and%20higher%20per%20capita%20income%20than%20the%20national%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20over%20a%20quarter%20of%20India's%20digital%20talent%2C%20Karnataka%20houses%20over%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20GCCs%20and%20around%2011%2C000%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721213880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2Ff7jcb1gk_computer-generic_625x300_04_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fkarnataka-job-quota-may-force-companies-to-relocate-software-body-nasscom-6125449%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20day%20after%20the%20Karnataka%20cabinet%20approved%20a%20bill%20mandating%20reservation%20for%20locals%20in%20the%20private%20sector%20jobs%2C%20software%20body%20Nasscom%20has%20sought%20its%20withdrawal%20saying%20the%20provisions%20%26quot%3Bthreaten%20to%20drive%20away%20companies%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fkarnataka-job-quota-may-force-companies-to-relocate-software-body-nasscom-6125449%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fkarnataka-job-quota-may-force-companies-to-relocate-software-body-nasscom-6125449%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fkarnataka-job-quota-may-force-companies-to-relocate-software-body-nasscom-6125449%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CBSE%20Brainstorms%20When%20And%20How%20To%20Conduct%20Board%20Exams%20Twice%20A%20Year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20CBSE%20is%20in%20a%20dilemma%20over%20scheduling%20the%20two%20rounds%20of%20board%20examinations%20as%20recommended%20in%20the%20new%20National%20Curriculum%20Framework%20(NCF)%20-%20its%20options%20being%20January-February%2C%20March-April%20and%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20option%20the%20Central%20Board%20of%20Secondary%20Education%20(CBSE)%20is%20exploring%20is%20a%20semester%20system%20involving%20biannual%20exams.%20Currently%2C%20the%20board%20exams%20for%20Classes%2010%20and%2012%20are%20conducted%20in%20February-March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20consultations%20are%20on%20and%20no%20decision%20has%20been%20made%20yet%20about%20when%20and%20in%20which%20format%20the%20plan%20to%20conduct%20board%20exams%20twice%20a%20year%20will%20be%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20three%20possible%20options%20that%20have%20been%20discussed%20is%20conducting%20the%20exams%20in%20a%20semester%20system%2C%20with%20the%20first%20board%20exam%20in%20January-February%20and%20the%20second%20one%20in%20March-April%20or%20conducting%20the%20second%20set%20of%20board%20exams%20in%20June%20with%20the%20supplementary%20or%20improvement%20exams%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20our%20academic%20calendar%20is%20designed%2C%20plus%20the%20schedule%20of%20competitive%20exams%20and%20geographical%20challenges%20since%20CBSE%20schools%20are%20spread%20across%20the%20country%20and%20even%20abroad%2C%20the%20semester%20system%20seems%20less%20feasible%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20board%20has%20told%20the%20Union%20education%20ministry%20that%20more%20than%20150%20steps%20are%20required%20to%20conduct%20board%20exams%20of%20Classes%2010%20and%2012%20in%20the%20current%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20process%20involves%20a%20minimum%20of%20310%20days%2C%20starting%20from%20filling%20of%20the%20list%20of%20candidates%2C%20centre%20notifications%2C%20release%20of%20roll%20numbers%2C%20conduct%20of%20practicals%2C%20theory%20exams%2C%20result%20declaration%2C%20verification%20and%20revaluation.%20At%20least%2055%20days%20are%20required%20to%20conduct%20the%20two%20exams%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20board%20has%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20before%20the%20CBSE%20now%20is%20when%20to%20replicate%20the%20massive%20exercise%20for%20a%20second%20round%20and%20how.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConducting%20exams%20before%20February%20also%20has%20its%20own%20challenges%20because%20some%20states%20have%20difficult%20winters.%20Currently%2C%20the%20schedule%20of%20board%20exams%20begins%20around%20February%2015%2C%20so%20dates%20have%20to%20be%20worked%20out%20accordingly%20to%20provide%20a%20considerable%20gap%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnother%20option%20can%20be%20to%20conduct%20the%20second%20set%20of%20exams%20in%20June%20alongside%20the%20supplementary%20or%20improvement%20exam.%20However%2C%20none%20of%20these%20options%20are%20final.%20We%20are%20still%20brainstorming%20and%20widespread%20consultations%20are%20on.%20It%20is%20possible%20that%20more%20options%20would%20emerge%20during%20the%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry's%20initial%20plan%20was%20to%20introduce%20biannual%20board%20exams%20from%20the%202024-25%20academic%20session.%20However%2C%20it%20has%20been%20pushed%20back%20by%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrepared%20by%20the%20Union%20government-appointed%20national%20steering%20committee%2C%20led%20by%20former%20ISRO%20chairman%20K%20Kasturirangan%2C%20in%20line%20with%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020%2C%20the%20new%20NCF%20proposed%20a%20semester%20system%20for%20students%20of%20Classes%2011%20and%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20framework%2C%20which%20was%20released%20by%20the%20ministry%20in%20August%20last%20year%2C%20also%20proposed%20that%20students%20be%20given%20the%20option%20to%20write%20their%20board%20exams%20twice%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Education%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20told%20PTI%20in%20an%20interview%20last%20October%20that%20appearing%20for%20board%20exams%20twice%20a%20year%20won't%20be%20mandatory%20for%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20students%20will%20have%20the%20option%20of%20appearing%20for%20the%20(class%2010%20and%2012%20board)%20exams%20twice%20a%20year%20just%20like%20the%20engineering%20entrance%20exam%20JEE.%20They%20can%20choose%20the%20best%20score%2C%20but%20it%20will%20be%20completely%20optional%2C%20no%20compulsion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20first%20attempt%20at%20reforming%20board%20exams.%20The%20Continuous%20and%20Comprehensive%20Evaluation%20(CCE)%20was%20introduced%20for%20Class%2010%20in%202009%20but%20was%20revoked%20in%202017%20and%20the%20board%20reverted%20to%20the%20old%20model%20of%20year-end%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20board%20exams%20for%20Classes%2010%20and%2012%20were%20also%20split%20into%20two%20terms%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20as%20a%20one-time%20measure%2C%20but%20the%20old%20format%20of%20year-end%20exams%20resumed%20this%20year.