ul%3E%3Cli%3EChinese%20firms%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20making%20job%20applicants%20take%20pregnancy%20tests.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EProsecutors%20in%20Jiangsu%20investigated%2016%20companies%20in%C2%A0Nantong%2C%20according%20to%C2%A0%C2%A0Procuratorial%20Daily.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20contradicts%20China's%20push%20for%20higher%20pregnancy%20rates%20amid%20declining%20national%20birth%20rates.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Chinese%20companies%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20introducing%20a%20controversial%20and%20illegal%20new%20step%20to%20their%20recruitment%20process%3A%20Pregnancy%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20in%20Nantong%2C%20a%20city%20in%20the%20province%20of%20Jiangsu%2C%20investigated%2016%20companies%20which%20they%20said%20had%20168%20candidates%20take%20pregnancy%20tests%20as%20part%20of%20physical%20pre-employment%20exams%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20state-run%20outlet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewspaper.jcrb.com%2F2024%2F20240715%2F20240715_007%2F20240715_007_2.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProcuratorial%20Daily%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20cited%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F07%2F17%2Fbusiness%2Fchina-firms-illegal-pregnancy-tests-intl-hnk%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F3270586%2Fchinese-firms-caught-carrying-out-illegal-pregnancy-tests-female-jobseekers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%20(SCMP)%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tongzhou%20district%20launched%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20unnamed%20companies%20earlier%20this%20year%20after%20being%20tipped%20off%20by%20a%20public%20litigation%20group%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20said%20they%20looked%20into%20a%20physical%20exam%20center%20and%20two%20hospitals%2C%20the%20latter%20of%20which%20reported%20that%20the%20women%20were%20only%