nce%20of%20a%20comeback.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20remark%20by%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20that%20triggered%20speculation%20that%20all%20is%20not%20well%20within%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government.%20The%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20has%20trashed%20this%20buzz.%20%26quot%3BThe%20organisation%20is%20bigger%20than%20the%20government.%20No%20one%20is%20bigger%20than%20the%20organisation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Maurya%20said%20at%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20state%20BJP%20working%20committee%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20remark%2C%20which%20following%20Mr%20Maurya's%20meeting%20with%20BJP%20president%20JP%20Nadda%2C%20was%20widely%20seen%20as%20a%20veiled%20swipe%20at%20Mr%20Adityanath.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20infighting%20in%20the%20government.%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20fighting%20among%20themselves.%20The%20people%20know%20about%20the%20corruption%20and%20are%20fed%20up%20with%20the%20game%20of%20thrones%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20at%20a%20party%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20had%20earlier%20said%20that%20the%20administration%20had%20been%20put%20on%20the%20back%20burner%20as%20the%20state's%20BJP%20leaders%20compete%20with%20each%20other.%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20engineered%20splits%20in%20other%20parties%2C%20is%20now%20doing%20the%20same%20within.%20This%20is%20why%20it%20is%20sinking%20in%20the%20quicksand%20of%20infighting.%20There%20is%20no%20one%20in%20the%20BJP%20to%20think%20for%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20buzz%20surrounding%20Mr%20Maurya's%20remark%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%20the%20BJP%20%26quot%3Bwants%20to%20stand%20with%20those%20who%20lost%26quot%3B.%20Mr%20Maurya%2C%20a%20former%20UP%20BJP%20chief%2C%20lost%20the%202022%20Assembly%20election%20but%20was%20retained%20as%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister.%20He%20is%20now%20a%20member%20of%20the%20legislative%20council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%2C%20Mr%20Maurya%20tweeted%20this%20afternoon%20that%20the%20BJP's%20governments%20and%20organisation%20in%20the%20country%20and%20the%20state%20are%20strong.%20%26quot%3BThe%20return%20of%20SP's%20reign%20of%20goons%20in%20UP%20is%20impossible.%20BJP%20will%20repeat%202017%20in%20the%202027%20state%20polls%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20X.%20Significantly%2C%20Mr%20Maurya%20was%20state%20BJP%20chief%20in%202017%20and%20the%20BJP%20had%20scored%20a%20thumping%20win%20in%20that%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20BJP%20state%20leaders'%20meet%2C%20Mr%20Adityanath%20had%20said%20%26quot%3Boverconfidence%26quot%3B%20cost%20the%20BJP%20dearly%20in%20the%20recently-held%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20results%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20came%20as%20a%20rude%20shock%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20this%20general%20election%2C%20its%20score%20dropping%20from%2062%20in%202019%20to%2033%20this%20time.%20The%20Samajwadi%20Party%20made%20huge%20gains%20to%20bag%2037%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20percentage%20of%20votes%20that%20was%20in%20favour%20of%20BJP%20in%202014%20and%20subsequent%20elections%2C%20BJP%20has%20been%20successful%20in%20getting%20the%20same%20number%20of%20votes%20in%202024%20as%20well%2C%20but%20the%20shifting%20of%20votes%20and%20overconfidence%20have%20hurt%20our%20expectations%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adityanath%20said%2C%20calling%20upon%20party%20workers%20to%20step%20up%20preparations%20for%20the%20upcoming%20bypolls%20in%2010%20Assembly%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20said%20he%20was%20confident%20of%20a%20good%20show%20by%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20in%20the%20bypolls%2C%20the%20date%20of%20which%20has%20not%20been%20announced%20yet.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20upcoming%20state%20budget%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Centre%20says%20we%20are%20the%20fifth-largest%20economy%20globally.%20And%20UP%20talks%20about%20a%201%20trillion%20dollar%20economy.%20The%20state%20government%20should%20tell%20us%20how%20much%20the%20Centre%20has%20helped%20in%20this%20case.%20The%20government%20in%20Delhi%20must%20put%20out%20the%20per%20capita%20income%2C%20if%20we%20become%20the%20third-largest%20economy%2C%20will%20we%20be%20able%20to%20match%20per%20capital%20income%20in%20developed%20countries%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20drawn%20a%20Kalyan%20Singh%20parallel.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20an%20experience%20of%2044%20years%20in%20UP...%20The%20same%20thing%20is%20happening%20now%20when%20Kalyan%20Singh%20was%20removed%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20only%20time%20will%20tell%20if%20there%20is%20another%20Kalyan%20Singh%20or%20if%20Kalyan%20Singh%20can%20overpower.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20and%20see%20why%20all%20this%20is%20happening.%20But%20one%20thing%20is%20sure%3A%20the%20honest%20BJP%20workers%20are%20really%20sad%20inside%2C%26quot%3B%20Congress%20leader%20Pramod%20Tiwari%20has%20said%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20downplayed%20the%20issue.%20Union%20Minister%20BL%20Verma%20said%20there%20is%20no%20infighting%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20and%20the%20organisation%20are%20doing%20their%20work.%20The%20organisation%20and%20the%20government%20compliment%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721211660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fniqosmgo_akhilesh-yadav_625x300_17_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fakhilesh-yadav-yogi-adityanath-up-fed-up-with-game-of-thrones-akhilesh-yadav-amid-bjp-infighting-buzz-6124845%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20people%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20are%20fed%20up%20with%20infighting%20within%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath-led%20BJP%20government%2C%20main%20Opposition%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20leader%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%20today.%22%2C%22