68%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElizabeth%20opted%20to%20take%20a%20course%20in%20welding%20rather%20than%20going%20to%20college.%3Cp%3EElizabeth%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20finished%20school%20and%20the%20introductory%20course%2C%20I%20sent%20out%20a%20bunch%20of%20resumes.%20I%20already%20had%20some%20industry%20contacts%20%E2%80%94%20from%20part-time%20trade%20work%20I'd%20done%20during%20high%20school%2C%20so%20finding%20a%20job%20was%20a%20little%20easier%20for%20me%20than%20for%20some%20of%20my%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20people%20were%20chasing%20the%20highest-paid%20jobs%2C%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20get%20my%20foot%20in%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mentality%20was%3A%20get%20experience%20first%2C%20the%20money%20will%20come%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20managed%20to%20do%20that%2C%20and%20I've%20jumped%20around%20various%20welding%20jobs%20since%20graduating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-you-should-become-electrician-apprenticeship-job-growth-career-trend-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eless%20physical%20trades%20like%20electrical%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I%20like%20how%20tough%20welding%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20killing%20my%20body%20every%20day%2C%20but%20it's%20worth%20it%20because%20welders%20make%20insane%20money%2C%20and%20I'm%20getting%20jacked%20doing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20constantly%20moving%20and%20climbing%2C%20so%20my%20abs%20are%20getting%20more%20ripped%2C%20and%20my%20butt%20is%20getting%20bigger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20see%20the%20hard%20work%20paying%20off%20physically%3B%20it's%20great%20for%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20covered%20in%20bruises%20and%20scratches%20from%20the%20job%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20definitely%20pretty%20beat%20up.%20But%20it%20makes%20me%20super%20strong%2C%20and%20getting%20to%20work%20outside%20is%20a%20real%20perk.%20Earning%20money%20while%20spending%20time%20out%20in%20the%