icut%2520Sun%2520vs%2CWNBA%2520game%2520on%2520ESPN%2520ever.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eviewership%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20attendance%2C%20her%20play%20hasn't%20been%20at%20quite%20the%20same%20level%20it%20was%20in%20college.%20In%20her%20rookie%20season%2C%20Clark%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.basketball-reference.com%2Fwnba%2Fplayers%2Fc%2Fclarkca02w.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaveraging%3C%2Fa%3E%20roughly%2017%20points%20and%20eight%20assists%20per%20game%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20the%20Fever%20and%20shooting%2033%25%20from%20three-point%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Matheson%20said%20ticket%20demand%20for%20the%20team's%20home%20games%20could%20increase%20as%20Clark%20and%20her%20team%20progress%20this%20season%20and%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come.%20The%20Fever%20have%20the%20WNBA's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wnba.com%2Fstandings%3Fseason%3D2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseventh-best%3C%2Fa%3E%20record%20so%20far%20this%20season%20among%2012%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20her%20skill%20grows%20and%20her%20team%20improves%2C%20she%20has%20a%20real%20chance%20to%20turn%20from%20a%20novelty%20into%20a%20true%20superstar%20where%20fans%20both%20at%20home%20and%20away%20can't%20get%20enough%20of%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20Matheson%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20time%20will%20tell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f77c1dfa-46e2-48e4-802b-4d8192879ad7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Fever%20have%20a%20bigger%20stadium%20than%20most%20WNBA%20teams%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20limited%20number%20of%20opportunities%20for%20road%20fans%20to%20see%20Clark%20play%20isn't%20the%20only%20supply-demand%20factor%20that%20could%20be%20impacting%20ticket%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWNBA%20arenas%20with%20more%20seats%20can%20sell%20more%20tickets.%20If%20two%20arenas%20have%20the%20same%20level%20of%20ticket%20demand%2C%20the%20one%20with%20more%20seats%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecould%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20have%20lower%20ticket%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20maximum%20seating%20capacity%20of%20nearly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportskeeda.com%2Fus%2Fwnba%2F5-wnba-stadium-largest-seating-capacity%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E18%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20fans%2C%20the%20Fever's%20Gainbridge%20Fieldhouse%20in%20Indianapolis%20%E2%80%94%20also%20home%20to%20the%20NBA's%20Indiana%20Pacers%20%E2%80%94%20is%20the%20fifth%20biggest%20arena%20in%20the%20WNBA%20among%20its%2012%20teams%2C%20per%20the%20sports%20content%20platform%20Sportskeeda.%20The%20average%20capacity%20of%20a%20WNBA%20arena%20is%20about%2012%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20it's%20possible%20the%20Fever's%20above-average%20arena%20size%20could%20be%20helping%20to%20keep%20home%20prices%20in%20check%20%E2%80%94%20and%20their%20opponents's%20smaller%20arenas%20could%20be%20propping%20up%20the%20prices%20of%20the%20team's%20road%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Matheson%20said%20this%20doesn't%20tell%20the%20whole%20story.%20In%20part%2C%20that's%20because%20some%20WNBA%20teams%20with%20smaller%20seating%20capacities%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcchicago.com%2Fnews%2Fsports%2Fwnba-teams-bigger-arenas-host-caitlin-clark-fever%2F3426538%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Las%2520Vegas%2520Aces%2520and%2Cindicates%2520it%2527s%2520a%2520smart%2520move.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Editched%3C%2Fa%3E%20their%20arenas%20when%20the%20Fever%20came%20to%20town%20so%20they%20could%20accommodate%20more%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFever%20opponents%20have%20been%20frequently%20moving%20home%20games%20against%20Clark%20into%20larger%20arenas%2C%26quot%3B%20Matheson%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20the%20Washington%20Mystics%20moved%20their%20June%207%20game%20out%20of%20the%20Entertainment%20and%20Sports%20Arena%20into%2020%2C000-plus%20seat%20Capital%20One%20Arena%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wusa9.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fwashington-m