%2Fmiddle-east%2Fgulf-states-condemn-rare-oman-attack-claimed-by-jihadists%2Famp_articleshow%2F111806686.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20A%20Small-Town%20Kannadiga%20Brought%20India%20Its%201st%20Miss%20Universe%20Petite%20Crown%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EImagine%20doing%20a%2036-hour%20shift%20in%20a%20hospital%20and%20then%20turning%20up%20willingly%20the%20next%20day%20to%20chip%20away%20the%20imperfections%20to%20become%20a%20beauty%20queen%3F%20That%20is%20what%20Shruti%20Hegde%2C%20a%20doctor%20and%20a%20beauty%20queen%20from%20Hubli%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20has%20been%20doing%20since%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Kannadiga's%20hard%20work%20has%20paid%20off%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20little%20over%20a%20month%20ago%2C%20on%20June%2010%2C%20Shruti%20Hegde%20became%20India's%20first%20Miss%20Universal%20Petite%2C%20a%20pageant%20that%20was%20started%20in%202009%20to%20give%20opportunity%20to%20shorter%20women%2C%20who%20found%20themselves%20often%20dwarfed%20by%20the%20amazonian%20standards%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20height.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pageantry%20is%20held%20in%20Tampa%2C%20Florida%20in%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%2C%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20not%20easy%20for%20sure.%20I%20realised%20that%20being%20a%20doctor%20is%20a%20lot%20more%20work%20than%20I%20initially%20thought.%20Yes%2C%20it%20becomes%20too%20much%20at%20times.%20But%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20will%20be%20choosing%20one%20over%20the%20other.%20Instead%2C%20I%20want%20to%20find%20a%20balance%20between%20both%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Hegde%20to%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20took%20the%20pageantry%20route%2C%20Hegde%20said%20she%20never%20gave%20much%20thought%20to%20winning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20always%20wanting%20to%20do%20new%20things%2C%20and%20I%20guess%20it%20is%20almost%20every%20small-town%20girl's%20dream%20%E2%80%93%20to%20be%20a%20beauty%20queen.%20So%2C%20I%20thought%20I'll%20just%20give%20it%20a%20try.%20It%20helped%20that%20I%20had%20a%20mother%20who%20is%20keener%20than%20me%20that%20I%20should%20do%20what%20I%20want%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Hegde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20how%20Hedge%20found%20herself%20signing%20up%20for%20Miss%20Dharwad%20contest%20in%202018.%20But%20when%20she%20won%20the%20contest%2C%20things%20took%20a%20serious%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20course%20of%20the%20contest%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20I%20was%20learning%20a%20lot%20of%20life%20lessons%20too%20%E2%80%93%20the%20kind%20that%20will%20help%20me%20be%20a%20better%20person%20and%20be%20better%20equipped%20to%20tackle%20any%20kind%20of%20situation.%20So%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20give%20my%20all%20to%20it%2C%20and%20see%20where%20it%20took%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Hegde%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20pursuing%20MD%20in%20dermatology%20and%20working%20as%20an%20intern%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20Tumakuru%2C%20a%20city%20about%2070%20km%20away%20from%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20soon%20hit%20the%20next%20roadblock.%20Not%20only%20did%20a%20small%20town%20like%20Hubballi%20have%20the%20necessary%20means%20for%20all%20the%20preparations%20required%20to%20become%20a%20beauty%20queen%2C%20but%20she%20also%20had%20to%20take%20a%20break%20and%20deal%20with%20a%20medical%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202019%2C%20I%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20benign%20ovarian%20and%20uterine%20tumours%20and%20had%20to%20undergo%20open%20surgery.%20This%20ate%20up%20two%20years%20of%20my%20life%20%E2%80%93%202019%20and%202020%20%E2%80%93%20as%20I%20recuperated.%20I%20thought%20that%20was%20the%20end%20of%20my%20pageantry%20career%20for%20a%20while.%20Again%2C%20my%20mother%20wouldn't%20let%20me%20off%20so%20easily.%20She%20stood%20behind%20me%20like%20a%20rock%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Hegde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20Hegde%20said%20she%20bounced%20back%2C%20went%20tripping%20all%20over%20India%2C%20taking%20classes%20to%20get%20herself%20the%20poised%20look%20of%20a%20beauty%20queen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere's%20so%20much%20to%20it%20%E2%80%93%20diction%2C%20clothing%2C%20walking%E2%80%A6%20And%20initially%2C%20you%20will%20have%20to%20spend%20for%20all%20that%2C%20in%20lakhs%20and%20lakhs.%20But%20by%20now%20nothing%20could%20stop%20me%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20go%20all%20the%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Hedge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20she%20won%20a%20big%20title%20%E2%80%93%20the%20second%20runner%20up%20of%20Miss%20Asia%20International%20India%202023%20%E2%80%93%20financial%20strain%20lessened%20a%20lot%2C%20said%20Hegde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20getting%20sponsors%20for%20my%20clothes%20and%20stuff.%20Which%20was%20a%20relief%20because%20earlier%20I%20had%20only%20a%20couple%20of%20outfits%20that%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20wear%20to%20different%20pageantries%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hegde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20expected%2C%20pageantry%20opened%20other%20doors%20in%20the%20entertainment%20industry.%20Since%202023%2C%20Hegde%20said%20she%20has%20been%20receiving%20offers%20to%20act%20in%20serials%20and%20films.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAgain%2C%20I%20ventured%20into%20it%20cautiously.%20Started%20first%20with%20serials.%20But%20the%20film%20that%20I%20just%20finished%20shooting%20for%2C%20%E2%80%98Sharanara%20Shakti'%2C%20made%20me%20realise%20a%20film%20career%20may%20not%20be%20a%20bad%20thing%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Hegde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHegde%20said%20she%20just%20played%20a%20dancer%20in%20the%20period%20film%20that%20traces%20the%20life%20of%20the%2012th%20century%20philosopher%2C%20poet%20and%20social%20reformer%20Basavanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20that%20the%20Kannada%20film%20industry%20is%20again%20opening%20itself%2C%20making%20it%20possible%20for%20films%20like%20%E2%80%98Sharanara%20Shakti'.%20It's%20perhaps%20the%20best%20time%20to%20be%20an%20actor%20here.%20I%20have%20now%20decided%20to%20take%20that%20plunge%20and%20see%20where%20it%20goes%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Hegde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHegde%20added%20that%20she%20is%20shooting%20right%20now%20for%20%E2%80%98Janumadata'%2C%20another%20odd-ball%20film%20that%20explores%20the%20undercurrent%20of%20the%20tense%20relationship%20between%20a%20father%20and%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20play%20the%20lead%20this%20time%20%E2%80%93%20the%20girlfriend%20who%20encourages%20the%20guy%20to%20face%20things%20head-on%20even%20as%20he%20struggles%20to%20accept%20his%20father%20as%20he%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Hegde.%20PTI%20JR%20ROH%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721209320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F15ajknuo_shruti-hegde-miss-universe-petite-crown_625x300_17_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshruti-hegde-how-a-small-town-kannadiga-brought-india-its-1st-miss-universe-petite-crown-6124006%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Imagine%20doing%20a%2036-hour%20shift%20in%20a%20hospital%20and%20then%20turning%20up%20willingly%20the%20next%20day%20to%20chip%20away%20the%20imperfections%20to%20become%20a%20beauty%20queen%3F%20That%20is%20what%20Shruti%20Hegde%2C%20a%20doctor%20and%20a%20beauty%20queen%20from%20Hubli%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20has%20been%20doing%20since%202018.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshruti-hegde-how-a-small-town-kannadiga-brought-india-its-1st-miss-universe-petite-crown-6124006%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshruti-hegde-how-a-small-town-kannadiga-brought-india-its-1st-miss-universe-petite-crown-6124006%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshruti-hegde-how-a-small-town-kannadiga-brought-india-its-1