%20happy%20with%20him%20doing%20Engineering%20and%20just%20getting%20a%20good%20job!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvicky-kaushal-reveals-his-father-sham-kaushal-wanted-to-commit-suicide-when-he-was-jobless-despite-ma-in-english-he-was-ready-to-work-as-a-sweeper-in-mumbai%2Farticleshow%2F111805816.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rs%201%2C200%20Crore%20Needed%20For%20India's%20Electric%20Car%20Revolution%3A%20Top%20Scientist%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20big%20expectation%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Union%20Budget%20is%20enhanced%20incentives%20for%20electric%20vehicles.%20India%20is%20the%20global%20capital%20for%20air%20pollution%2C%20and%20e-mobility%20is%20a%20very%20promising%20way%20to%20reduce%20that%2C%20at%20least%20in%20big%20cities.%20India's%20chief%20scientist%20has%20released%20a%20new%20roadmap%20for%20research%20on%20e-mobility%2C%20asserting%20that%20if%20the%20government%20invests%20Rs%201.200%20crore%20in%20R%26amp%3BD%2C%20then%20in%20less%20than%20five%20years%2C%20India%20can%20aspire%20to%20lead%20in%20electric%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Ajay%20Kumar%20Sood%2C%20Principal%20Scientific%20Adviser%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20told%20NDTV%20that%20very%20soon%20internal%20combustion%20engines%20running%20on%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20will%20become%20extinct%20like%20dinosaurs%2C%20with%20electric%20vehicles%20becoming%20the%20preferred%20mode%20of%20transportation.%20Professor%20Sood%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20first%20half%20of%202024%2C%20nearly%209%20lakh%20electric%20vehicles%20were%20sold%20in%20India%2C%20but%20the%20penetration%20has%20to%20go%20up%20to%2030%20per%20cent%20by%202030.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20report%20titled%20%26quot%3Be-Mobility%20R%26amp%3BD%20Roadmap%20for%20India%26quot%3B%20was%20launched%20by%20Professor%20Sood.%20The%20R%26amp%3BD%20roadmap%20has%20been%20prepared%20after%20a%20detailed%20understanding%20of%20the%20global%20automotive%20sector%20and%20identifying%20future%20cutting-edge%20technological%20requirements.%20It%20categorises%20research%20projects%20into%20four%20important%20areas%3A%20energy%20storage%20cells%2C%20electric%20vehicle%20aggregates%2C%20materials%20and%20recycling%2C%20and%20charging%20and%20refuelling%2C%20providing%20clear%20pathways%20to%20attain%20global%20leadership%20by%20being%20Atmanirbhar%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20electric%20vehicles%20to%20become%20affordable%20and%20popular%2C%20a%20big%20breakthrough%20is%20really%20required%20in%20battery%20technology.%20Professor%20Sood%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BResearch%20on%20sodium-ion%20batteries%20and%20aluminum-ion%20batteries%20looks%20promising.%26quot%3B%20Making%20cheaper%2C%20lighter%2C%20safer%2C%20and%20longer-lasting%20batteries%20is%20the%20real%20key%20to%20the%20successful%20adoption%20of%20electric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Sood%20highlighted%20that%20India%20aims%20to%20achieve%20a%2045%20per%20cent%20reduction%20in%20emission%20intensity%20by%202030%20and%20energy%20independence%20by%202047%20to%20reach%20net-zero%20commitment%20by%202070.%20A%20significant%20part%20of%20this%20vision%20will%20require%20the%20wider%20adoption%20of%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20indigenous%20energy%20storage%20systems%2C%20and%20the%20generation%20of%20renewable%20energy%20to%20feed%20charging%20infrastructures.%20He%20said%20that%20presently%2C%20the%20e-mobility%20value%20chain%20heavily%20depends%20on%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20e-mobility%20R%26amp%3BD%20roadmap%20charts%20a%20course%20towards%20future%20independence%20and%20self-sufficiency%2C%20outlining%20critical%20research%20initiatives%20that%20will%20position%20India%20as%20a%20leader%20in%20the%20global%20value%20and%20supply%20chains%20within%20the%20next%20five%20to%20seven%20years.%20This%20roadmap%20aims%20to%20fill%20critical%20gaps%20in%20the%20current%20research%20and%20development%20framework.%20While%20many%20identified%20projects%20are%20yet%20to%20achieve%20global%20success%2C%20some%20areas%20already%20demonstrate%20significant%20international%20accomplishments%20and%20India%20is%20yet%20to%20commence%20preparations.%20These%20projects%20are%20included%20to%20establish%20a%20strong%20foundation%20for%20the%20country%20to%20pursue%20future%20innovations%20in%20those%20areas%20when%20opportunities%20arise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Sood%20said%20that%20the%20automobile%20sector%20in%20India%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20contributors%20to%20the%20country's%20GDP%2C%20and%20considering%20its%20fast%20growth%20trajectory%2C%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so%20in%20the%20future.%20He%20emphasized%20that%20this%20progress%20should%20be%20aligned%20with%20the%20Net-Zero%20vision%20of%20the%20country%20and%20that%20there%20is%20an%20impending%20need%20to%20foster%20a%20culture%20of%20R%26amp%3BD%20and%20innovation-driven%20growth%20in%20the%20automotive%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Karthick%20Athmanathan%2C%20lead%20author%20of%20the%20report%20and%20Professor%20of%20Practice%20at%20IIT%20Madras%2C%20said%20that%20India%20%26quot%3Bneeded%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20current%20import-dependent%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEasier%20said%20than%20done%2C%20but%20Professor%20Sood%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BBeing%20self-sufficient%20is%20most%20important%2C%20and%20India%20can%20become%20a%20leader%20in%20the%20global%20electric%20vehicle%20supply%20chain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721207880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F6qdhcm3o_professor-sood-_625x300_17_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-1-200-crore-needed-for-indias-electric-car-revolu