C%20and%2020%20percent%20coco%20peat%20to%20prepare%20a%20potting%20mix%20that%20will%20ensure%20vegetables%20receive%20sufficient%20nutrition%20for%20growth.%20Adding%20homemade%20manure%20or%20vermicompost%20to%20this%20mix%20enhances%20the%20soil%E2%80%99s%20fertility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%20the%20top%20five%20vegetables%20that%20thrive%20in%20the%20rainy%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Tomatoes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETomatoes%20are%20perfect%20for%20beginners.%20They%20can%20be%20grown%20in%20small%20containers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECut%20small%20slices%20of%20tomatoes%20or%20simply%20add%20seeds%20to%20a%20small%20pot.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECover%20them%20lightly%20with%20soil%20and%20sprinkle%20water%2C%20maintaining%20consistent%20moisture.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWater%20the%20plant%20regularly%2C%20but%20if%20the%20soil%20is%20moist%2C%20you%20can%20water%20at%20intervals%20of%20one%20or%20two%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKeep%20the%20seedlings%20out%20of%20direct%20sunlight%20and%20rainwater.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAs%20the%20plant%20grows%2C%20add%20homemade%20manure.%20You%20can%20prepare%20a%20natural%20fertiliser%20using%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fhow-to-turn-pomegranate-mango-orange-peels-into-fertilisers-for-your-garden%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efruit%20peels%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Soak%20the%20peels%20in%20water%20for%20a%20week%2C%20then%20strain%20out%20the%20water%20and%20add%20it%20to%20the%20plants.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUse%20cow%20dung%20fertiliser%20during%20the%20flowering%20stage.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20tomatoes%20will%20be%20ready%20to%20harvest%20in%20about%20three%20months.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Pumpkin%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPumpkins%20can%20be%20planted%20during%20July-August.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESow%20see