0grow%20grains%20on%20his%20three-acre%20land.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20that%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20very%20profitable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20team%20from%20Earthy%20Tales%20visited%20his%20farm%20about%20three%20years%20back%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20start%20growing%20vegetables%20on%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20land.%20As%20this%20started%20giving%20him%20a%20good%20return%2C%20today%20he%20grows%20cucumbers%2C%20chillies%20and%20other%20vegetables%20in%20his%20entire%20farm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20income%20has%20increased%20almost%20four%20times%20after%20the%20interventions%20from%20Earthy%20Tales%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC8gpzxVSN_A%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC8gpzxVSN_A%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC8gpzxVSN_A%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Earthy%20Tales%20Organics%20(%40earthytales.in)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farm-to-fork%20company%20has%20trained%20over%20500%20farmers%20so%20far.%20It%20is%20incubated%20by%20the%20government%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Agriculture%E2%80%99s%20Rashtriya%20Krishi%20Vikas%20Yojana%20(RKVY)%20%E2%80%93%20Remunerative%20Approaches%20for%20Agriculture%20and%20Allied%20sector%20Rejuvenation%20(RAFTAAR)%20scheme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarthy%20Tales%20has%20also%20set%20up%20two%20farmer%20training%20and%20collection%20centres%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20with%20Deepak%20delivering%20products%20twice%20a%20week%20in%20his%20car%20now%20delivers%20products%20twice%20a%20day%20in%20Delhi-NCR%20and%2011%20other%20cities.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20become%20a%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20best%20friend%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Deepak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Deepak%20Sabharwal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721055035000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-08-at-14.20.28-min-1721051668.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D356941%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Deepak%20Sabharwal%20was%20shocked%20to%20read%20the%20'poison'%20label%20on%20pesticides%20used%20on%20his%20family's%20farms.%20He%20shifted%20to%20organic%20farming%20and%20started%20Earthy%20Tales%2C%20with%20a%20mission%20to%20help%20more%20farmers%20make%20the%20switch.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmer%20Earns%205%20Times%20More%20with%20Hydroponics%20%26amp%3B%20Saves%2080%25%20on%20Electricity%20Bills%3B%20Helps%20Others%20Switch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUntil%202016%2C%20Pritpal%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20family%20in%20Chandigarh%20had%20been%20cultivating%20wheat%20and%20paddy%20for%2050%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20culture%20of%20monocropping%20is%20prevalent%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20where%20most%20families%20grow%20paddy%20and%20wheat%20throughout%20both%20Kharif%20and%20Rabi%20seasons.%20Sticking%20to%20specific%20crops%20year%20after%20year%20eventually%20leads%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20soil-borne%20diseases%20and%20substantially%20decreases%20the%20fertility%20of%20soil%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritpal%20was%20always%20intrigued%20by%20new%20ways%20to%20make%20farming%20more%20profitable%20and%20reduce%20the%20risks%20associated%20with%20traditional%20agricultural%20practices.%20This%20quest%20led%20him%20to%20quit%20his%20three-year%20long%20corporate%20career%20and%20turn%20to%20farming.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CComing%20from%20a%20family%20of%20farmers%2C%20I%20was%20always%20connected%20to%20my%20roots%2C%20even%20during%20my%20higher%20studies%20in%20Nagpur%20and%20my%20job%20in%20Mumbai.%20Whenever%20I%20got%20a%20chance%2C%20I%20visited%20my%20farm%2C%20contemplating%20how%20to%20transform%20it%20into%20a%20profitable%20venture%20for%20the%20next%20generation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20told%20my%20parents%20about%20my%20decision%20to%20pursue%20farming%20full-time%2C%20their%20first%20concern%20was%20also%20about%20the%20new%20approaches%20I%20wanted%20to%20try%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20MBA%20graduate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritpal%20went%20on%20to%20turn%20his%20ancestral%20farm%20into%20a%20thriving%20business%20with%2025%2C000%20green%20leafy%20plants%20such%20as%20lettuce%20and%20spinach%20flourishing%20in%20an%208%2C000%20square-feet%20area.%20Every%20month%2C%20he%20harvests%20up%20to%20800%20kg%20of%20leafy%20greens%2C%20achieving%20five%20times%20the%20yield%20compared%20to%20conventional%20farming%20while%20using%20fewer%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20possible%20due%20to%20the%20protected%20cultivation%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336600%2Ftech-nursery-hydroponics-aeroponics-farming-ratlam-brothers-arbind-ravindra-dhakad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esystem%20of%20hydroponics%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhere%20crops%20are%20grown%20without%20soil!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20soil%20borne%20diseases%20such%20as%20fungal%20and%20bacterial%20infections%20that%20affect%20crop%20yield.%20You%20cannot%20eliminate%20microorganisms%20and%20parasites%20like%20nematodes%20from%20the%20soil.%20So%2C%20I%20thought%20of%20eliminating%20soil%20itself%20as%20a%20medium%20altogether.%20I%20turned%20to%20hydroponics%2C%20which%20eliminates%20this%20worry%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritpal%20now%20grows%20exotic%20leafy%20greens%20such%20as%20Italian%20basil%2C%20baby%20spinach%2C%20three%20to%20four%20kinds%20of%20lettuces%2C%20vine%20crops%20like%20red%20and%20yellow%20capsicum%20and%20seedless%20cucumbers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20grows%20these%20crops%20in%202.5%20acres%20of%20land%20comprising%20multiple%20types%20of%20protected%20environment%20structures%2C%20including%20an%20indoor%20vertical%20farm%2C%20a%20temperature-controlled%20polyhouse%2C%20a%20naturally-ventilated%20polyhouse%2C%20and%20indoor%20and%20outdoor%20hydroponics%20setups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FPritpal-4-1721052314.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pritpal%20grows%20leafy%20greens%20like%20lettuce%20and%20vegetables%20like%20capsicum.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FPritpal-4-1721052314.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FPritpal-4-1721052314-300x157.jpg