0growth%2C%20unlike%20in%20open-field%20farming%20where%20large%20quantities%20of%20fertilisers%20are%20used%20without%20control%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritpal%20says%20that%20he%20invested%20Rs%2060%20lakh%20in%20setting%20up%20the%20whole%20system%20on%20a%202.5%20acre%20farm.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20this%20is%20only%20a%20one-time%20investment%2C%20yielding%20recurring%20benefits%20throughout%20the%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20he%20grows%20leafy%20greens%20hydroponically%20and%20harvests%20up%20to%20800%20kg%20of%20produce%20every%20month.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20leafy%20greens%2C%20the%20yield%20is%20almost%20five%20times%20greater%20compared%20to%20traditional%20land-based%20farming.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20beauty%20of%20hydroponics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPritpal%20also%20grows%20bell%20peppers%20and%20seedless%20cucumbers%20in%20a%20naturally-ventilated%20polyhouse%20spanning%20across%201.5%20acres.%20Annually%2C%20he%20harvests%20up%20to%2090%20tonnes%20of%20seedless%20cucumbers%20and%20up%20to%2030%20tonnes%20of%20bell%20peppers.%20%E2%80%9CI%20get%20a%2030%20percent%20higher%20return%20in%20this%20setup%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FPritpal-5-1721052345.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hydroponic%20farming%20provides%20precise%20control%20over%20nutrient%20delivery%20leading%20to%20increased%20crop%20yields.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FPritpal-5-1721052345.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FPritpal-5-1721052345-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FPritpal-5-1721052345-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20h