0can%20be%20altered%20to%20suit%20local%20palates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProof%20lies%20in%20a%20MasterChef%20Australia%20Season%2013%20episode%20in%202021%20where%20Indian-origin%20home%20chef%20Depinder%20Chhibber%20made%20%3Cem%3Ekathi%20%3C%2Fem%3Erolls%2C%20adding%20a%20twist%20to%20them%20by%20making%20the%20snack%20out%20of%20crayfish%20and%20deep%20lobster%20%3Cem%3Emasala%20%3C%2Fem%3Ealong%20with%20egg%2C%20pickled%20onions%2C%20mint%2C%20coriander%20chutney%2C%20fresh%20carrots%2C%20capsicum%2C%20and%20coriander%20leaves.%20She%20served%20the%20rolls%20with%20mint%20and%20coriander%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20tomato%20%3Cem%3Ekasundi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F200958%2Fkasundi-mustard-sauce-queen-of-pickles-bengal-traditional-food-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20traditional%20Bengali%20sauce%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCP0TDIMDGSD%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCP0TDIMDGSD%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2