20original%20ones%20or%20just%20add%20stickers%20stating%20that%20it%20is%20from%20Devgad.%20To%20combat%20this%2C%20we%20applied%20for%20a%20GI%20tag%2C%20which%20we%20received%20in%202018%2C%E2%80%9D%20Omkar%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20GI%20tag%20is%20meant%20to%20protect%20the%20intellectual%20property%20of%20the%20producer%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20farmer%2C%20and%20the%20place%20of%20origin%2C%20Devgad.%20It%20is%20additionally%20meant%20to%20benefit%2C%20enforce%20quality%20and%20prevent%20adulteration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20lower%20quality%20mangoes%20which%20were%20being%20sold%20under%20the%20name%20of%20Devgad%20Hapus%20affected%20the%20Devgad%20brand.%20We%20wanted%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349604%2Fhow-to-grow-japanese-mango-miyazaki-at-home-in-odisha-engineer-garden-with-rare-flower-fruit-plants-1000-petal-lotus%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestablish%20the%20source%20and%20quality%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20tried%20barcode%20printing%2C%20edible%20ink%2C%20magnetic%20patterns%20and%20several%20other%20methods.%20They%20were%20all%20getting%20replicated%20by%20fakes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20one%20needs%20to%20understand%20is%20that%20the%20Devgad%20mango%20has%20a%20unique%20flavour%20due%20to%20the%20topography%20of%20the%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDevgad%20has%20hard%20laterite%20rocks%2C%20which%20gives%20the%20fruits%20a%20splendid%20aroma.%20The%20high%20altitude%20gives%20it%20its%20unique%20taste%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Omkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESantosh%20Patkar%2C%20a%20farmer%2C%20states%20that%20what%20differentiates%20the%20Devgad%20variety%20from%20the%20ones%20found%20in%20Ratnagiri%20and%20other%20regions%20is%20its%20taste%2C%20colour%2C%20thin%20skin%2C%20and%20minimal%20fibre%20percentage.%20Speaking%20about%20the%20identity%20crisis%2C%20he%20shares%20that%20people%20are%20selling%20fake%20Devgad%20mangoes%20even%20after%20their%20production%20is%20over%20for%20the%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20are%20selling%20mangoes%20from%20Karnataka%20and%20calling%20it%20Devgad%20Hapus.%20Retailers%20and%20online%20stores%20are%20duping%20people%20while%20charging%20a%20bomb.%20Due%20to%20this%2C%20our%20rate%20and%20value%20is%20also%20coming%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20it%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20the%20problem%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F260907%2Findia-gi-tag-konkan-alphonso-mango-farmers-income%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQR%20codes%20or%20bar%20codes%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20that%20it%20can%20be%20copied.%20Prashant%20Yadav%2C%20an%20engineer%20and%20founder%20of%20Sun%20Solutions%2C%20developed%20the%20patented%20technology.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimply%20put%2C%20the%20unique%20code%20of%20each%20product%20is%20divided%20into%20two%20parts%2C%20one%20above%20the%20seal%20and%20one%20below%20it.%20To%20access%20the%20entire%20code%2C%20one%20would%20have%20to%20tear%20the%20sticker%2C%20effectively%20keeping%20away%20counterfeits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdevgad-tag-1720776024.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tamper-proof%20sticker%20on%20real%20Devgad%20mangoes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdevgad-tag-1720776024.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdevgad-tag-1720776024-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdevgad-tag-1720776024-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdevgad-tag-1720776024-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdevgad-tag-1720776024-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356706%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20tamper-proof%20sticker%20on%20real%20Devgad%20mangoes%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20patent%20is%20for%20hiding%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20unique%20code.%20We%20divide%20each%20code%20into%20two%20parts%2C%20with%20one%20half%20hidden%20below%20the%20sticker.%20There%20are%20two%20digits%20below%20the%20sticker.%20Customers%20can%20take%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20label%20and%20send%20it%20the%20number%20mentioned.%20You%20can%20then%20tear%20off%20the%20sticker%20and%20send%20the%20remaining%20two%20digits%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Prashant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20software%20analyses%20the%20image%20and%20confirms%20through%20the%20database%20whether%20the%20product%20is%20one%20of%20theirs%20or%20not.%20The%20entire%20code%20is%20matched%20with%20the%20additional%20two%20digits%20sent%20as%20a%20caption%20on%20WhatsApp.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrashant%20received%20the%20patent%20in%202021%20for%20the%20tamper%20preventive%20seal.%20It%20is%20single%20use%20and%20can%20be%20authenticated%20by%20customers%20through%20WhatsApp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20help%20the%20brand%20equity%20of%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355301%2Fgrowing-miyazaki-mango-on-terrace-udupi-home-gardener-joseph-lobo-chikoo-berries-jasmine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Devgad%20Hapus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Omkar.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20also%20help%20the%20next%20generation%20continue%20farming%20as%20they%20can%20rea