unable%20to%20clear%20it%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20perfectly%20fine%20to%20explore%20other%20opportunities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F308203%2Fhow-to-prepare-for-upsc-cse-for-working-professionals-ias-divya-mittal-shares-tips-on-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlongside%20your%20job%2C%20you%20can%20prepare%20for%20this%20exam%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Hard%20work%20never%20goes%20to%20waste%3B%20I%20can%20attest%20to%20this%20after%20almost%2010%20years%20of%20my%20journey%2C%20which%20fortunately%20culminated%20in%20success%20in%20this%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20he%20began%20preparing%20for%20forest%20services%20alongside%20his%20full-time%20job.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20this%20was%20my%20last%20opportunity%20to%20get%20into%20the%20service%2C%20I%20was%20nervous.%20But%20finally%2C%20I%20tasted%20success%20in%20my%20first%20attempt%20at%20IFS%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Harsimran%2C%20who%20clenched%20an%20AIR%20of%2016%20in%20the%202022%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIAS%20vs%20IFS%20%E2%80%94%20How%20different%20is%20the%20preparation%20process%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20UPSC%2C%20candidates%20can%20choose%20their%20preferred%20ranks%2C%20opting%20for%20either%20IAS%2C%20IFS%2C%20or%20both.%20They%20have%20separate%20attempts%20for%20each.%20Initially%2C%20Harsimran%20focused%20solely%20on%20IAS%20(CSE).%20However%2C%20on%20his%20final%20attempt%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20pursue%20IFS%2C%20a%20decision%20that%20proved%20fruitful%20as%20he%20successfully%20cleared%20it%20on%20his%20first%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20changes%20that%20he%20made%20in%20his%20strategy%20before%20appearing%20for%20forest%20services%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20cutoff%20for%20the%20forest%20service%20exam%20is%20generally%20higher%20than%20that%20for%20civil%20services%2C%20requiring%20candidates%20to%20put%20in%20more%20effort%20right%20from%20the%20preliminary%20stage.%20I%20had%20to%20elevate%20my%20Prelims%20preparation%20to%20a%20whole%20new%20level.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-2-1720617509.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harsimran%20secured%20210%20marks%20out%20of%20300%20in%20the%20personality%20test%20round.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-2-1720617509.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-2-1720617509-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-2-1720617509-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-2-1720617509-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-2-1720617509-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356341%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarsimran%20secured%20210%20marks%20out%20of%20300%20in%20the%20personality%20test%20round.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20prepare%20effectively%2C%20I%20searched%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F282477%2Fupsc-cse-syllabus-previous-years-question-paper-tips-ias-officer-anisha-shrivastav%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUPSC%20question%20papers%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20This%20helped%20me%20understand%20UPSC%E2%80%99s%20expectations%20and%20gauge%20the%20adequacy%20of%20my%20preparation.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20focused%20on%20mastering%20subjects%20